According to the present invention, a distinction is made between:



    

the compounds of formula (I) in which R3 represents a hydroxyl (reference IA) and the other substituents A, X, R1, R2, R4 and R5 are as defined for a compound of formula (I);

the compounds of formula (I) in which R3 represents a group —NR7R8 (reference IB) and the other substituents A, X, R1, R2, R4, R5, R7 and R8 are as defined for a compound of formula (I);


in the form of a base or of salts of addition with acids or bases.

Among the compounds of formula (I) according to the invention, we may notably mention the following compounds:


