in which R4=phenyl, by reaction with phenylboronic acid in the presence of a palladium catalyst such as tetrakis(triphenylphosphine)palladium(0);

in which R4=—NR9R10, by reaction with an amine HNR9R10 in the presence of a copper(I) catalyst such as copper(I) iodide;

in which R4=CN, by reaction with zinc(II) cyanide and in the presence of a catalyst such as tetrakis(triphenylphosphine)palladium(0).

